    Mt. Arashi (Arashiyama) has lots of blooming cherry trees now, in this view looking west along the Katsura River* towards the Togetsu Bridge.&lt;br/&gt; 
    *The Katsura River changes name to the Oi River beyond the bridge. Further upstream it changes name again, to the Hozugawa River. &lt;em&gt;Yes, it&apos;s confusing. &lt;/em&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
  嵐山では今、桜がたくさん咲いています。桂川 (※) 沿いに西の渡月橋方面を見たところです。
&lt;br/&gt;
 ※ (桂川は橋のところで大堰川と名を変える。さらに上流では保津川と名を変える。)
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Panoramas" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">Mt. Arashi (Arashiyama) has lots of blooming cherry trees now, in this view looking west along the Katsura River* towards the Togetsu Bridge. *The Katsura River changes name to the Oi River beyond the bridge. Further upstream it changes name again, to the Hozugawa River. Yes, it&apos;s confusing.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07208-Pano-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07208-Pano-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Over the Hozugawa・保津川の上空</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220407/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Over the Hozugawa・保津川の上空" /><published>2022-04-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hozugawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220407/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    An aerial photograph over the Hozugawa river in Arashiyama, showing the cherry trees in bloom on Mr. Arashi.
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    嵐山の保津川上空で、嵐山に咲く桜を空撮したものです。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Aerial" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">An aerial photograph over the Hozugawa river in Arashiyama, showing the cherry trees in bloom on Mr. Arashi.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_DJI_0215.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_DJI_0215.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Himeji Castle・姫路城</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220406/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Himeji Castle・姫路城" /><published>2022-04-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/himeji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220406/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Himeji Castle, my favorite of all of Japan&apos;s castles, surrounded by cherry blossoms.
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 桜に囲まれた姫路城。
&lt;/p&gt;

