    Cherry blossoms are in full bloom everywhere you go in Kyoto these days. This is the Osawa Pond, part of Daikakuji Temple, surrounded by cherry blossoms in bloom. 
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 最近の京都は、どこへ行っても桜が満開です。これは、大覚寺の一部である大沢池で、満開の桜に囲まれています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Ponds" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms are in full bloom everywhere you go in Kyoto these days. This is the Osawa Pond, part of Daikakuji Temple, surrounded by cherry blossoms in bloom.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06983.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06983.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Tamagawa River・玉川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220404/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Tamagawa River・玉川" /><published>2022-04-04T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-04T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tamagawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220404/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    We went to the town of Ide in southern Kyoto Prefecture, about halfway between Uji and Nara. There were many cherry trees in full bloom along the Tamagawa River; a scene repeated along many rivers, all over Japan. A beautiful sight.
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 京都府の南部、宇治と奈良のほぼ中間に位置する井手町へ行った。玉川沿いにたくさんの桜が咲いていました。これは日本中の多くの川で繰り返されている光景です。美しい光景だ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Rivers" /><summary type="html">We went to the town of Ide in southern Kyoto Prefecture, about halfway between Uji and Nara. There were many cherry trees in full bloom along the Tamagawa River; a scene repeated along many rivers, all over Japan. A beautiful sight.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06920.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06920.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Osaka Castle・大阪城</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220403/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Osaka Castle・大阪城" /><published>2022-04-03T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-03T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/osaka-castle</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220403/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Cherry blossoms at Osaka Castle Park.
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
   大阪城公園で桜の花。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Osaka" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Castles" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms at Osaka Castle Park.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06867.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06867.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kamogawa Delta・鴨川デルタ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220402/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kamogawa Delta・鴨川デルタ" /><published>2022-04-02T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-02T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/delta</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220402/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Panorama from the Kamo Ohashi Bridge, looking north at the convergence of the Kamogawa River (left) and the Takano River (right).
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
   賀茂大橋から北を望み、鴨川（左）と高野川（右）の合流点を撮影したパノラマ写真です。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Kamogawa River" /><category term="Panoramas" /><summary type="html">Panorama from the Kamo Ohashi Bridge, looking north at the convergence of the Kamogawa River (left) and the Takano River (right).</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06842-Pano-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06842-Pano-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sakura Arashiyama・嵐山の桜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220401/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sakura Arashiyama・嵐山の桜" /><published>2022-04-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-01T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220401/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Cherry blossoms are in almost full bloom in Arashiyama.
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    嵐山では桜がほぼ満開です。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms are in almost full bloom in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06696.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R06696.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Night, Lights &amp;amp; Flowers・夜と灯りと花</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220331/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Night, Lights &amp;amp; Flowers・夜と灯りと花" /><published>2022-03-31T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-31T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nijo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220331/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
